'''范汕洄''' （{{bd|1972年||}}）是一位美国华人电子工程师，材料学家，光学工程师。<ref name="StanfordEngineering">{{cite journal |last1=Abate |first1=Tom |title=In addition to making energy, what if solar panels could save energy? |url=https://engineering.stanford.edu/magazine/article/addition-making-energy-what-if-solar-panels-could-save-energy |journal=Stanford Engineering: Research & Ideas |date=2018 |accessdate=July 23, 2019 }}</ref>

==生平==
1972年出生于[[河南|河南]][[郑州|郑州]]，1988年毕业于[[广东实验中学|广东实验中学]]，1992年毕业于[[中国科学技术大学|中国科学技术大学]]，1997年获得[[麻省理工学院|麻省理工学院]]博士学位。之后继续留校开展博士后工作。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://academictree.org/chemistry/peopleinfo.php?pid=63207|title=Chemistry Tree: John D. Joannopoulos|access-date=2019-07-23}}</ref>2001年4月加入[[斯坦福大学|斯坦福大学]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.stanford.edu/news/2001/june20/prezreport-620.html
|title=Stanford Report: President's report to the Board of Trustees|website=news.stanford.edu/news/2001/june20/prezreport-620.html|access-date=2019-07-23}}</ref>2012年担任[[悉尼大学|悉尼大学]]物理学访问教授。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sydney.edu.au/ipos/images/content/research/IPOS-Annual-Report-2012-13.pdf
|title=University of Sydney: Institute of Photonics and Optical Science|website=sydney.edu.au/ipos/images/content/research/IPOS-Annual-Report-2012-13.pdf|access-date=2019-07-23}}</ref>截至2019年已经发表57项专利。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://patents.justia.com/search?q=shanhui+Fan&page=7|title=Search Patents - Justia Patents Search|website=patents.justia.com}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.crunchbase.com/person/shanhui-fan|title=Shanhui Fan - Co-Founder @ Skycool Systems|website=Crunchbase}}</ref>

